item.title: Stunning Restaurant
item.dc:creator: cardinalwp
item.content:encoded: Went for the early bird for a birthday meal. The owner was very friendly and the staff were efficient, we even got a free garlic bread. The three course menu is good value for money and there is plenty of choice. Portion sizes were also good. The surroundings are very pleasant and the place is clean. It got busy for a Monday night which speaks volumes about a place. I would return.

item.title: Really Impressed, Would Recommend!
item.dc:creator: cardinalwp
item.content:encoded:
Went with my husband to celebrate my birthday in January. The staff are friendly and attentive, the food is superb and the wine was delicious. I had steak which was cooked as I requested. 

I would recommend to anyone.
